T16D4408:345b-0: @345b ` // stong chen mo rab tu 'joms pa las gsungs pa'i smon lam bzhugs//
T16D4408:345b-2: # // dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16D4408:345b-3: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzi brjid dang //
T16D4408:345b-4: rang rgyal dag gi gzi brjid dang //
T16D4408:345b-5: dgra bcom rnams kyi mthu dag dang //
T16D4408:345b-6: gsang sngags 'dzin pa thams cad dang //
T16D4408:345b-7: sh'a ri'i bu yi shes rab dang //
T16D4408:345b-8: mood gal bu yi rdzu 'phrul dang //
T16D4408:345b-9: ma 'gags pa yi mig dang ni //
T16D4408:345b-10: 'od srungs sbyangs pa'i yon tan dang //
T16D4408:345b-12: kun dga' bo yi thos pa dang //
T16D4408:345b-13: tshangs pa yi ni byams pa dang //
T16D4408:345b-14: rgya byin gyi ni dbang rnams dang //
T16D4408:345b-15: 'jig rten skyong gi yul rnams dang //
T16D4408:345b-16: dbang phyug chen po'i stobs rnams dang //
T16D4408:345b-17: sde dpon rnams kyi mthu dag dang //
T16D4408:345b-19: de dag rnams kyi mthu dang gzis //
T16D4408:345b-20: bdag gi dug ni dug med shog /'phags pa stong
T16D4408:345b-21: chen po rab tu 'joms pa las gsungs pa'i smon
